professor at Harvard.

00:02:14.950 --> 00:02:18.650
-I'm writing a book this year on
the rise of democracy in Europe

00:02:18.650 --> 00:02:19.240
historically.

00:02:19.240 --> 00:02:20.741
-So like who the people are.

00:02:20.741 --> 00:02:22.490
